MOST IMMEDIATE
No.1/34/1/2018-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 13th November, 2018
The undersigned is directed to say that consequent upon the demise of Shri Ananthkumar,
Minister of Chemicals and Fertilizers; and Minister of Parliamentary Affairs on the 12th November,
2018:
Shri D.V. Sadananda Gowda assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of Chemicals
and Fertilizers. He will continue to hold the charge of the office of the Minister of Statistics
(i)
and Programme Implementation.
(ii)
Shri Narendra Singh Tomar assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of
Parliamentary Affairs. He will continue to hold the charge of the office of the Minister of Rural
Development; Minister of Panchayati Raj; and Minister of Mines.
(Bhaskar Dasgupta)
for Cabinet Secretary
Tel: 2379 2204
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded for information to the Vice-Chairperson, NITI Aayog.
(Bhaskar Dasgupta)
for Cabinet Secretary
Copy forwarded for information to:
Secretary to the President.
Secretary to the Vice-President.
(Bhaskar Dasgupta)
Director

Principal Secretary to the Prime Minister.

(Bhaskar Dasgupta)
